transcripts.text: May the Lord make his face to shine upon us and be gracious unto us.  May the Lord lift up the light of his countenance upon us and give us peace.  Peace in our families, peace across this land, and dare I ask, O Lord, peace even in this chamber, now and evermore.  We ask it in the name of the monotheistic God, Brahma, and God known by many names by many different faiths.  a man and a woman.
